Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:13.36,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,My life has suddenly become \Na lot more lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.36,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,The reason couldn't be clearer:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:17.47,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,because we're a family of four now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.90,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Shall we read a book, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:20.74,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.83,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I love the books you read \Nto me! They're so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:28.33,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Then let's read Lauretta's {\i1}History of\Nthe Rise and Fall of the Elvish People: Vol. 3{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:30.67,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,chapter 5, passage 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:34.57,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,the commercial policy failures of the \N Clar Dynasty of the province of Hrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:36.11,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's way too specialized!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:40.33,Main - Top,Shalsha,0,0,0,,The private army of Kranke, the first ruler \Nof the Clar Dynasty, grew so mighty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:44.56,Main - Top,Shalsha,0,0,0,,that it attained the status of a military \Nclique among the elves of Hrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:48.40,Main - Top,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Eventually, in the year 405, \Nhe declared himself king.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:49.31,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Elves, huh? I've never met an elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:53.50,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Boing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:54.14,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:55.22,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Boing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:00:58.71,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:00.61,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,It's an elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:02.70,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,And what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:05.90,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Um, someone is after me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:09.58,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,and I was hoping the Witch of \Nthe Highlands could help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:12.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I bet I can guess who \Nwould go after an elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:15.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Are there any orcs around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.93,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It's not orcs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:20.37,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I want you to save me from \Nthe high demon Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:21.58,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm not home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.91,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Wait! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:30.30,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I don't know of anyone who could help \Nme but the Witch of the Highlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:32.82,Main - Top,Azusa,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight a monster that scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.81,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Please don't say that! I heard \Nyou're incredibly strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:37.76,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:41.77,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, Most Powerful, \NBerserk, Wonderful, Strong Witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:44.82,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Don't give me weird names that \Nmake me sound like a wrestler!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:46.14,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Bzzz...
