Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:26.58,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I came here from a small nation of \Nelves in the province of Hrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:30.09,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm Halkara the apothecary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:31.52,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Apothecary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.52,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,It's someone who makes medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.59,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's similar to my line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.93,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Yes, witches make medicines, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.72,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I specialize in plants, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:44.42,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, now we know what you do for a living,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.61,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,but why would Beelzebub want \Nto go after an apothecary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:52.26,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm one of the \Nhighest-paid apothecaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:56.11,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I collected components of mushrooms and \Nplants with exceptional nutritional value
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.99,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,to make an alcoholic drink \Ncalled Nutri-Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:00.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Nutri-Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.19,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,When you're tired, \Njust one bottle of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.57,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,...clears your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.54,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,...strengthens your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.46,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Halkara's Nutri-Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.17,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It'll get you through your tough job!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:12.83,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Hustle charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.86,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's just an energy drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.85,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sure, I had a lot of them when \NI pulled all-nighters, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:20.85,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Nutri-Spirit became popular everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.72,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,making it an explosive hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:26.76,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I even started a factory in town, \Nbut production still couldn't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:29.38,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It's just that successful and profitable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:31.42,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.76,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,And why is Beelzebub after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:37.61,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Apparently, she acquired some and drank it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:40.60,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,but it seems to be poisonous to demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:43.49,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,After drinking it, she passed \Nout with a high fever
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.86,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,and nearly ended up going straight to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:48.13,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,A demon... going to Hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:52.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So you're saying Beelzebub is \Nholding a grudge over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:53.63,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:59.13,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,She's been fuming that she'll kill \N"whoever made this vile poison."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:02.69,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It got me chased out of my own town!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.36,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I have nowhere to go anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.34,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Please! You have to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.69,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama, I feel so bad for the elf lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:14.89,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I can't bear to see someone \Nwith no home to go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,All right. I'll help y—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.86,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.22,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You changed your tune quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:25.41,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But I have no intention \Nof fighting Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:26.61,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'll only shelter you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:31.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,When you go out, wear this robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:35.85,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,The story is that you're the second \Npupil of Azusa, Witch of the Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:39.08,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Thank you, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.80,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:41.92,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Boing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:47.11,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... It's just a bit tight on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.34,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This might not work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Halkara, has anyone ever told \Nyou that you're very well-developed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:55.47,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,About 750 times a year or so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's about twice a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.15,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Bzzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.87,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You who have wicked hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:05.58,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,be caught in this net and \Nbecome incapacitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:09.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This net will fall upon you as \Nif it has a will of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.90,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,There. That doesn't look too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:20.69,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Now Beelzebub won't be able to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.22,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.95,Main,All,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.48,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Um, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.66,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,When I was busy with work, \NI ate out all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:42.86,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,and when I was being chased, I survived \Non tree nuts I found in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:47.61,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It's been so long since I had a warm \Nmeal like this with anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.11,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Halkara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:54.34,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Halkara, have some of this \Nraspberry jam. It's my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:58.20,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:05.06,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sorry to have you gather \Nmedicinal herbs with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:07.78,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I bet the ones around here are \Ndifferent from yours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.24,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.32,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Ah! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:13.24,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,A dawn king mushroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.89,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,This one's a greater round mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.38,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,And these are rolling rat mushrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.95,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're only picking mushrooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:22.08,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Well, mushrooms are my specialty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.77,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Please be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:27.15,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Some of these are poison mushrooms \Nthat are dangerous to eat raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.65,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,But take this one, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:34.62,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,If you boil it for about ten minutes, \Nthe poisons break down and disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.77,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Then you can use them for cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:37.78,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:41.02,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,By the way, the poison gives \Nyou a warm, fuzzy feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.37,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,so connoisseurs leave a bit \Nin them when cooking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.63,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,That mushroom's borderline insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:52.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This herb-gathering was way more \Nproductive than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:53.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.90,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Not at all. I'm glad you \Nhad such a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:01.11,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like the small ones are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.54,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,This called elvin sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:08.39,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It's made by fermenting \Nseveral types of beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.27,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,It smells like soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:18.11,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.20,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Please eat all you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:24.42,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I had no idea there were \Nso many edible mushrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:29.18,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,We elves don't live in \Nthe forest for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:36.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'd love to teach the villagers how to make \Noptimal use of the forest's bounties, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.48,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,That's a nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I need to get my daughters \Nand Laika to try it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:45.55,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'll be glad to provide all \Nthe guidance you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:49.56,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Come on, you're laughing a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:53.91,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,You're right... But I just can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:55.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:59.63,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Halkara, are those poison \Nmushrooms you're eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:04.43,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? \NI'm a mushroom expert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.48,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Striped wave mushrooms don't contain poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.89,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Orange pencil mushrooms don't \Ncontain poison, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.60,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Triangular chestnut mushrooms \Ndo contain poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You did have a poisonous one in the mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.73,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:20.76,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I put one from the \Nmedicinal-use zone in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.31,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Your sorting method's too careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:25.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's one I haven't eaten yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.68,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's a silver lining, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.19,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I did eat one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What symptoms does it cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:37.02,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It stimulates your mind and body \Nso you laugh uncontrollably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:42.03,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,And... it works as an aphrodisiac, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.97,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh? Aphrodisiac?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:48.42,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,That means it temporarily \Nmakes you feel very lewd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:49.38,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:54.18,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Why are you moving away, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.47,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Because I suspect you're \Nfull of poison right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.36,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.14,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Jiggle, jiggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:02.31,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Would you like to do something fun with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.59,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Actually... please do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:05.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:10.75,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I promise \Nit'll make you feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.70,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm worried about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.56,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:22.84,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:23.82,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:24.64,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:26.08,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:29.97,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Um... What happened while you \Ntwo were gathering herbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.59,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I neutralized the poison with magic, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.03,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I made a careless mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:39.05,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please don't ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:41.60,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Accept these mushroom dishes as my apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.15,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.49,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,It's wonderfully seasoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:47.84,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:48.95,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:51.83,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Striped wave mushrooms puff up \Nwhen you wrap them before cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.32,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,They're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.48,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You bounced back quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:58.02,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Our cooking repertoire will \Nexpand with you here, Halkara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.60,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.09,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Bzzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:08.08,Eyecatch,Title,0,0,0,,I've Been Killing {\c&HE4AE06&}Slimes\N{\c&H313536&}for {\c&HE4AE06&}300 Years {\c&H313536&}and\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Maxed Out {\c&H313536&\3c&HFFFFFF&}My {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Level
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:16.79,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master, you're so quick at defeating slimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:19.18,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I've been doing it for 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:21.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, Halkara, give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.14,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:23.88,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Bob!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.75,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:26.52,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Boing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:27.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:28.81,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.94,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I managed to defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.85,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wow, check it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.87,Main,Old,0,0,0,,Thank you for this blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.60,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So... do you always get stared at this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:41.86,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:44.55,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It's sort of my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.92,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,You should have more confidence, \Ntoo, even if you're small.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:50.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I-I'm not that small!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:51.82,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:55.79,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It does seem curious that there are \Nmore women staring at you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:12:01.66,Main,Natalie,0,0,0,,Oh, an adventurer put that up this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:02.97,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:04.17,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,A "wanted" notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:08.02,Main,Natalie,0,0,0,,The reward for it is quite generous, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:10.75,Main,Natalie,0,0,0,,I guess those who have it, have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.97,Main,Natalie,0,0,0,,and those who don't... don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:17.86,Main - Top,Natalie,0,0,0,,I do all kinds of mundane \Ntasks, day in and day out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,"Searching for a female apothecary \Nin the province of Hrant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:18.65,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,who makes a product called Nutri-Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.68,Main - Top,Natalie,0,0,0,,Maybe I should become an adventurer, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.68,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Goes by the name Halkara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.60,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,She is currently on the run from Hrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:27.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Most notable physical feature: \Nher very large chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:32.51,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Reward of 15 million gold for \Nthe one who captures her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.88,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Posted by the demon Beelzebub."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.20,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,She's already made her move...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:41.54,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,At least we have the lack of a physical \Ndescription going in our favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But it's just a matter of \Ntime before she comes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:49.90,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Laika, can you evacuate my daughters \Nto some village far from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:51.27,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:53.88,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Mother, I want to fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.57,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Your willingness alone is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:12:58.83,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.64,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Shalsha, don't make things \Ndifficult for Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.80,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,You might think what you're saying \Nmakes you a good daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.66,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,but that's not what being \Na good daughter means.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.70,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Okay, Big Sister. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:11.66,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Good girl, Shalsha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.25,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thanks, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.57,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Now, we must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:22.06,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I will revert to my dragon form \Nat once and take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:22.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:30.56,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I hope the barrier I put up \Nthis morning keeps her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.80,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Bzzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:37.16,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Please don't let anything happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:45.99,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Having Nutri-Spirit on hand makes \Nme feel like I can fight all night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.42,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I can't believe you can drink \Nthat at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:51.80,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,The whole concept of my medicine-making
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.74,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,is to make things I'd \Nwant to consume myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.58,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,You're drinking it yourself, \Naren't you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:00.48,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I haven't had any.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.42,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:03.02,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,But look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I really didn't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.97,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Also, Halkara, did you eat dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.15,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What? No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.82,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Th-This is a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.21,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I wouldn't joke at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.35,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Bzzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.79,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Bzzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:17.90,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:19.13,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:21.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub is a fly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:22.75,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Bzzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:25.70,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Yes, she's also known as \Nthe Lord of the Flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.46,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm just wondering here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:31.90,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,C-Certainly not! \NThat's just a filthy little fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:35.05,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It's a lowly creature that \Nswarms around horse poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.81,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,There's no way it's a \Nterrifying demon like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.90,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a lowly creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:44.84,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master, don't start doing \Ncrazy voice impersonations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.57,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.80,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Then whose voice was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.26,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.45,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,My name is Beelzebub.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.52,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Excuse me for being nothing \Nbut a lowly creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.18,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,"Lowly creature" was just \Na figure of speech!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.73,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I am but a speck of dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:15.34,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I had no intention of saying such a \Nthing about a great being like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:20.27,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It is that speck of dust \Nthat I came here to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:24.70,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You've been hiding out in this \Nhouse all along, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.07,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.92,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I've been making myself at \Nhome since she arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:31.47,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Why didn't you reveal yourself right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:35.84,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I wanted to make sure this \Nwoman truly was Halkara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:39.45,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Also, flying around in houses \Nin the form of a fly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:42.60,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,is my favorite way to spend \Nmy extended vacations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.97,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's pretty unique!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:50.88,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Halkara, I went through \Ngreat pains to find you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.69,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,but it was very much worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:56.94,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Please spare me! I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:58.05,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:01.87,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Anything, you say? \NThat is what my ears heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:07.64,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,All dealings with my pupil will \Nhave to be made through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:08.67,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:12.63,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Witch of the Highlands, \Nyou intend to stand in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:15.75,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,My pupil doesn't seem \Ninterested in seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.38,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'll have to ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:22.33,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,When told to leave, it is only natural \Nthat I want to leave even less.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:26.03,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Or... do you wish to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.35,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:32.61,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I haven't fought in so long, \NI was starting to get rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:35.03,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let's fight fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:37.03,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,My thoughts exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.05,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll go over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:51.66,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this? A mere human \Nis bound to regret defying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.90,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I will show you just how terrifying \Nthe power of a high demon is—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.12,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:07.67,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Did you not say we would \Nfight fair and square?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.02,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.93,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Uh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:15.86,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I didn't think it would work when \Nyou tried to {\i1}leave{\i0}, too... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:16.65,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.49,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You think apologizing will help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:21.38,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Honestly, talk about raining on my parade...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.00,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I challenge you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:27.59,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Uh, aren't you exhausted already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:29.67,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Please! This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.87,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I feel ill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:37.35,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,And I'm having chills...\Nand I feel a bit nauseous...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.44,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I... can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.60,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.81,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Halkara, help me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.15,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.18,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Making healing magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:53.77,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:18:00.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,God of the earth, it is not yet known \Nwhether your chaotic power is good or evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.29,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Grant that power unto me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.41,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.57,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hey, is healing magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:09.04,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,something you can use on a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:11.89,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Huh? I think... it should be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:15.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay! If it's not, I blame you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.52,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,That's too heavy a burden to bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:22.90,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Her color looks a bit better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:25.28,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,All right! We're gonna keep doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.65,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master, she's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.95,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:37.68,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Yes, the nausea has subsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.07,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,And the chills are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:40.68,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.21,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You just need to rest for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:47.98,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Witch of the Highlands, \NI thought you were a coward,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.33,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,but you are quite the remarkable woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:54.50,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If you died on me because of that, \NI'd regret it for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:59.39,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Once I recover, I'd like to \Ndrink your Nutri-Spirit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.16,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:03.09,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But if you do, it might \Nalmost kill you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.27,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:09.22,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I heard that you developed a high fever \Nand nearly died after drinking it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.50,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:14.20,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I drank it during an all-nighter, \Nand it filled me with the drive to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.39,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I took it too far and overworked myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:18.31,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,which caused me to break out in a fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.60,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,but only because I put too \Nmuch stress on my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.15,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:24.16,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Your Nutri-Spirit is loved
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:27.93,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,not only by the Devil himself, \Nbut by all demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:31.55,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Which is why I came to ask \Nyou to make some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:33.67,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,S-So that's what you wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:37.02,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,That's all? What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:42.39,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.63,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:49.19,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved that it \Nwas a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:52.01,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I made another careless mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:55.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, I'm just glad I didn't \Nend up fighting for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.80,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,That's great, Halkara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.81,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Now you can make Nutri-Spirit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:02.05,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Oh, about that..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:05.81,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I was thinking of relocating \Nmy factory to this province.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Moving it here? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:10.08,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Because even if it was all a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:15.38,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I don't want to pay exorbitant taxes \Nto the town that abandoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.62,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:21.63,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Also... if I stay here, I can \Nlive with you, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:25.34,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, we still have rooms, so that's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But we all take turns doing \Nthe cooking and cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.18,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Of course! I'll work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.06,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,That sounds rather fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.60,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.26,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Witch of the Highlands, Azusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.96,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I have yet to settle my score with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.96,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Next time, we'll fight without the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:43.88,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:48.17,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Of course, if you do anything else \Nthat's fun, you must invite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:51.62,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I'll teach you a spell to summon me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:52.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:54.39,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Beelzebub.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.50,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Have some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.37,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:21:00.25,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub, can we ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.36,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.93,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,What is the current state of demon society?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:08.42,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The same dynasty has persisted \Nfor several centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.93,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It is quite peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:11.51,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Are you married?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:13.86,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,D-Don't ask silly questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:16.89,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Only races that age quickly do such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:25.24,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Say... I'd like to adopt one of \Nthese two as my own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:28.00,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm honored, but I must decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:31.60,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Beelzebub, what kind of life do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:33.30,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Do you live as a fly all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:35.66,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,W-Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:37.70,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Things have gotten more lively here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:38.97,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,A dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:40.09,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.20,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,an elf,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:42.81,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,and a demon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:46.48,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,We're quite a crew, but it's starting \Nto feel like we're a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:47.17,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:52.15,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Amid the bustle, I get to \Nspend time taking it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:56.11,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,I was starting to think this \Nslow life would last forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:59.74,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,but then, a problem arose the very next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.08,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I will be returning to my own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.03,0:22:06.82,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Our family's falling apart!
